strings: <voice_0x0100130C><se_low>King Trode: Well, it seems we've arrived in Orkutsk at last!

<voice_0x0100130D><se_low>King Trode: And that nook grass really is quite marvellous!
I wasn't a bit cold even in all that snow!
<voice_0x0100130E><se_low>King Trode: Now we can stay outdoors as long as we like. Excellent! Well, I'll be waiting outside the town as usual. In you go!
